Card

Class Card

  • java.lang.Object
    • Card.Card
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CashTransferToPlayersCard, GetOutOfJailFreeCard, MoveToLocationCard, MoveToSpaceCard, RealEstateRepairCard, StaticCashTransferCard

    public abstract class Card
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the abstract base class for all the other card classes. It contains the information needed by all card objects including: text description, cardID, player who drew the card, and if it is a chance or community chest card
